    {
      "id": "n3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 2,
      "text": "The Goethe B1 writing module lasts 60 minutes in total and contains three tasks. Each Teil focuses on a different type of real-world interaction, mirroring the official exam structure."
    },
    {
      "id": "n4",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 3,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 1: Contact & Interaction"
    },
    {
      "id": "n5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 4,
      "text": "• Write a personal message that maintains or rebuilds contact"
    },
    {
      "id": "n6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 5,
      "text": "• Include a description, a reason, and a polite suggestion"
    },
    {
      "id": "n7",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 6,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 2: Expressing an Opinion"
    },
    {
      "id": "n8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 7,
      "text": "• Share your personal opinion on a given topic"
    },
    {
      "id": "n9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 8,
      "text": "• Support your view with explanations, comparisons, or examples"
    },
    {
      "id": "n10",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 9,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 3: Regulating a Situation"
    },
    {
      "id": "n11",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 10,
      "text": "• React to an everyday situation that requires coordination"
    },
    {
      "id": "n12",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 11,
      "text": "• Apologise, ask for something, or make a concrete request"
    },
